<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.6.6">
<l>pulaṉkoṇitik kuvaiyōṭu puḻaikkaimā kaḷiṟṟiṉamum</l>
<l>nalaṅkoṇava maṇikkuvaiyuñ cumanteṅkum nāṉṟocintu</l>
<l>kalaṅkaḷiyaṅ kummallaik kaṭaṉmallait talacayaṉam</l>
<l>valaṅkoḷmaṉat tāravarai valaṅkoḷḷeṉ maṭaneñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My simple heart, circle in prayer those with minds that circle in prayer</l>
<l>In Talacayaṉam at wealthy Mallai by the sea where boats move everywhere,</l>
<l>Dropping and sinking, bearing heaps of the excellent nine jewels,</l>
<l>Herds of huge trunked elephants, with heaps of gold that grab the senses.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
